description:
Jazz at Lincoln Center and JazzTimes awarded National Endowment for the Arts Jazz Master, pianist, composer, and educator Dr. Barry Harris as the recipient of the 2020 Bruce Lundvall Visionary Award. Dr. Harris was presented with the award by fellow NEA Jazz Master and friend Kenny Barron. 



https://www.facebook.com/jazzatlincolncenter/videos/2661337447317671/
title: Barry Harris at Jazz Congress 2020
